headline: S&P Global Launches AI-Ready Commodities Data Integrated With Microsoft 365 Copilot
summary: S&P Global (NYSE: SPGI) today announced the launch of AI agent capabilities that utilize data from the commodity sector, seamlessly integrated with Microsoft 365 Copilot and powered by S&P Global's Commodity Insights AI Ready Data solution.
